Roses aren't always red (#FF0000)
& violet arent exactly blue(#0000FF),
the society that we live in 
never seems to speak the truth.

Smiles aren't always happy
& frowns aren't always upset,
people judge too quickly
& our feelings are what they
              forget.
            :/fərˈɡet/
            >disremember,overlook,neglect
            [cease to think of or consider]
 
